# providerConfiguration

**Instance Property**

A dictionary containing keys and values defined by the Tunnel Provider developer.

## Declaration

```swift
var providerConfiguration: [String : Any]? { get set }
```

## Discussion

All of the keys and values in this dictionary must conform to the [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Foundation/NSSecureCoding] and [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Foundation/NSCopying] protocols.

## Accessing the tunnel configuration

- **providerBundleIdentifier**: A string identifying the specific Tunnel Provider extension that should be used with this configuration.
